Version 0.2.0 - 2025-09-26
- Added bilingual localization with English and Spanish copy surfaced via data tags.
- Introduced floating language toggles with fade interactions tied to the navigation panel.
- Persisted language preference and integrated switcher controls into the side panel layout.

